= class GLib::BufferedOutputStream

== Object Hierarchy

* Object
  * GLib::Instantiatable
    * GLib::Object
      * GLib::OutputStream
        * GLib::FilterOutputStream
          * GLib::BufferedOutputStream

== Class Methods

--- GLib::BufferedOutputStream.new

     * Returns: self: ((*FIXME*))

== Instance Methods

--- auto_grow

     * Returns: self: ((*FIXME*))

--- auto_grow=(auto_grow)

    Sets the value whether the buffer should automatically grow or not.
     * auto_grow: true if the buffer should automatically grow
     * Returns: auto_grow

--- auto_grow?

    Gets the value whether the buffer should automatically grow or not.
     * Returns: true if the buffer should automatically grow

--- buffer_size

    Gets the size of the backend buffer.
     * Returns: The size of the backend buffer

--- buffer_size=(buffer_size)

    Sets the size of the backend buffer.
     * buffer_size: The size of the backend buffer
     * Returns: buffer_size

--- set_auto_grow(auto_grow)

    Same as auto_grow=.
     * auto_grow: true if the buffer should automatically grow
     * Returns: self

--- set_buffer_size(buffer_size)

    Same as buffer_size=.
     * buffer_size: The size of the backend buffer
     * Returns: self

== Properties

--- auto-grow: true or false (Read/Write)

    Whether the buffer should automatically grow

--- buffer-size: Integer (Read/Write)

    The size of the backend buffer

